reviewText: Great collection of teen 80's movies. I bought these to watch with my 13 year old daughter as these were movies I watched as a teen. Perfect set. I'm so glad these 3 movies were in the same set. Great value! I ended up buying a second set for my niece.
This contains a great set of movies. Would suggest to anyone who like's movies of the 80"s.
great dvd, loving the old movies and sharing them with my kids. great price and value for what you get
